01:47:57.750 --> 01:47:59.791
<i>There's fear in all of us.</i>

01:47:59.958 --> 01:48:02.125
<i>I know that now.</i>

01:48:02.291 --> 01:48:05.125
<i>It's how you live with it
that makes you who you are.</i>

01:48:10.500 --> 01:48:13.291
<i>Years later, when
I got the news about Loonie,</i>

01:48:13.458 --> 01:48:15.416
<i>I can't say I was surprised.</i>

01:48:16.416 --> 01:48:18.750
<i>But it hit me... hard.</i>

01:48:21.166 --> 01:48:24.166
