to the back of the head.</i>

01:48:24.333 --> 01:48:26.333
<i>Some kind of drug deal
gone bad.</i>

01:48:31.125 --> 01:48:33.458
<i>He always lived
like he had nothing to lose.</i>

01:48:33.625 --> 01:48:35.625
<i>'Cause he thought
he didn't matter.</i>

01:48:41.250 --> 01:48:43.291
<i>Well, he mattered to me.</i>

01:48:48.291 --> 01:48:50.500
<i>I miss the mad bastard.</i>

01:49:01.625 --> 01:49:03.708
<i>I still paddle out
whenever I can.</i>

01:49:04.750 --> 01:49:08.291
<i>Not to prove anything.
Just... to feel it.</i>

01:49:09.375 --> 01:49:11.166
<i>That sweet momentum.</i>

01:49:11.333 --> 01:49:13.875
<i>The turning force under foot.</i>

01:49:15.083 --> 01:49:18.041
<i>And in those brief,
rare moments of grace...</i>

01:49:20.666 --> 01:49:22.208
<i>...I'm dancing.</i>

